GPIO Experiments on the BeagleBone Black.

Super bare bones implementation using the fs /sys/class/gpio.

Three Steps fs based BeagleBone GPIO:

1) Export the Pin
2) Set the direction
3) Write/Read the value.

--Implementation so far

//Exports the pin and sets the direction.
pinMode(ledPin, OUTPUT);

//Writes HIGH/LOW values to the suplied pin.
digitalWrite(ledPin, HIGH);

